lead_paragraph: Australian Marcus Fraser sank testing putts on his final two holes to land the European Tour's $3 million Maybank Championship Malaysia on Sunday after overnight leader Lee Soo-min fell apart down the stretch.

headline.print_headline: Fraser Lands Malaysia Title After Lee Falters
